# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Keep These Files (Force Include)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Keep important documentation
!README.md
!SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md
!CSV_IMPORT_FORMAT.md
!DATA_IMPORT_GUIDE.md
!TESTING_GUIDE.md
!CHANGELOG.md

# Keep requirements
!requirements.txt

# Keep manage.py
!manage.py

# Keep migration __init__.py files
!*/migrations/__init__.py

# Keep static source files (not collected staticfiles)
!static/

# Keep templates
!templates/

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Notes
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# This .gitignore file excludes:
# - Database files (db.sqlite3)
# - Python cache files (__pycache__)
# - Virtual environments (venv, env)
# - IDE configuration files (.vscode, .idea)
# - OS-specific files (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)
# - Collected static files (staticfiles/)
# - Media uploads (media/)
# - Log files (*.log)
# - Sensitive data (.env, *.key)
#
# To commit CSV files, comment out the CSV section above
# To commit batch files, comment out the batch file section above
# To ignore migrations, uncomment the migrations section above
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
